      "title": "Leopard carcass discovered from Nawalapitiya",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The carcass of the Sri Lankan leopard was discovered from an estate in Nawalapitiya on Thursday (25) morning.",
        "According to report, the dead leopard was disocovered trapped in a snare inside the Westhall Estate in Nawalapitiya.",
        "Wildlife Officers arrived on scene and took away the carcass of the some-what fully grown Sri Lankan leopard for further investigations.",
        "Army Chief Hails \u2018Commonwealth Games\u2019 winners; Yupun Abeykoon to be promoted",
        "Generator One of Norochcholai back in operation from Monday (29)"
